title: Hour 1 - NFL Week 7 Recap, World Series Preview
itunes:title: Hour 1 - NFL Week 7 Recap, World Series Preview
description:
Dan recaps the weekend in the NFL, specifically what's happening in Green Bay and Tampa Bay. And he wonders if anyone outside of Houston will  be rooting for the Astros against the Philadelphia Phillies in the World Series.
